has yet to start.

74
00:03:33,630 --> 00:03:36,260
You've surely congratulated me
too early.

75
00:03:36,770 --> 00:03:38,420
Believe me.

76
00:03:38,660 --> 00:03:40,660
You'll rank top in
the upcoming Imperial Examination.

77
00:03:42,090 --> 00:03:43,480
Brother Yue is really confident

78
00:03:43,480 --> 00:03:44,610
about my abilities.

79
00:03:44,850 --> 00:03:46,150
Of course!

80
00:03:46,790 --> 00:03:48,510
(You're the best scholar)

81
00:03:48,670 --> 00:03:50,560
(in my novel. The smartest one.)

82
00:03:50,890 --> 00:03:52,700
(I'm really happy to meet him here.)

83
00:03:53,060 --> 00:03:53,970
(I can't miss this opportunity.)

84
00:03:55,290 --> 00:03:56,930
Oh right, have you guys had your meal?

85
00:03:57,260 --> 00:03:58,220
How about

86
00:03:58,220 --> 00:03:59,790
