87
00:04:00,980 --> 00:04:02,460
(Zui Xiao Restaurant)

88
00:04:03,760 --> 00:04:05,490
Brother Yue, let me introduce you

89
00:04:06,650 --> 00:04:07,960
to Zhou Ren, or Brother Zhou.

90
00:04:08,790 --> 00:04:09,630
Nice to meet you.

91
00:04:11,290 --> 00:04:12,970
And this is Qian Si Xian,
or Brother Qian.

92
00:04:14,470 --> 00:04:16,160
These two are my classmates.

93
00:04:16,340 --> 00:04:17,480
We're here

94
00:04:17,760 --> 00:04:18,880
for the Imperial Examination.

95
00:04:19,310 --> 00:04:20,220
To be honest,

96
00:04:20,630 --> 00:04:22,030
I've studied for 15 years

97
00:04:22,030 --> 00:04:22,880
for the sole purpose

98
00:04:23,850 --> 00:04:26,330
of passing the Imperial Examination
to serve His Majesty

99
00:04:26,330 --> 00:04:27,120
and this country.

100
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:28,900
Although there are many great scholars

101
00:04:29,050 --> 00:04:30,210
who are attending

102
00:04:30,210 --> 00:04:31,010
the upcoming Imperial Examination,

103
00:04:31,370 --> 00:04:33,330
I'm confident about my abilities.

104
00:04:35,090 --> 00:04:35,890
I am determined to get the top rank.

105
00:04:36,830 --> 00:04:39,160
How inspiring! Let's have another drink!

106
